Lew Harvey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lew_Harvey 0 Lew Harvey (6 October 1887 – 19 December 1953) was an American film actor. He appeared in 145 films between 1918 and 1950. He was born in Wisconsin, educated in Portland, Oregon, and died in Los Angeles, California. Lew_Harvey ( 6_October_1887 – 19_December_1953 ) was an_American_film_actor .
